ai.skymind.pipelines.verticles.inference

Class InferenceVerticle

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.vertx.core.AbstractVerticle
      • ai.skymind.pipelines.verticles.base.BaseRoutableVerticle
        • ai.skymind.pipelines.verticles.inference.InferenceVerticle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Routable, io.vertx.core.Verticle

    public class InferenceVerticle
extends BaseRoutableVerticle
    A Verticle that takes multi part file uploads as inputs. Many computation graphs are usually multiple inputs by name: Each part for a multi part file upload should map on to a name. For example: input_1 : part name: input_1 input_2 : part name: input_2 The handler logic for this verticle is implemented in PipelineExecutioner
    Author:
    Adam Gibson
